32
00:04:10,627 --> 00:04:12,211
Slippery slope.

33
00:04:12,337 --> 00:04:15,006
Today, we withhold porn.
Tomorrow, it's clean bandages.

34
00:04:15,131 --> 00:04:17,508
Talk to Carlson in Denn,
he runs the budget committee,

35
00:04:17,884 --> 00:04:19,260
after you look at this.

36
00:04:19,385 --> 00:04:21,804
After you
talk to Carlson, maybe I'll...

37
00:04:21,930 --> 00:04:24,349
The patient is trapped
at the South Pole.

38
00:04:33,566 --> 00:04:35,443
Any possibility
of evacuating her?

39
00:04:35,568 --> 00:04:36,861
Well, that wouldn't be any fun.

40
00:04:36,986 --> 00:04:41,574
And for the next two months, winds make
it impossible to fly anything in or out.

41
00:04:41,699 --> 00:04:43,701
Could be appendicitis
or a gallstone.

42
00:04:43,826 --> 00:04:44,953
