45
00:04:50,291 --> 00:04:52,543
There's nothing we can do.
If it's a stone, she takes pain meds,

46
00:04:52,669 --> 00:04:54,504
stone passes.
There's nothing we need to do.

47
00:04:54,629 --> 00:04:56,506
Could be a struvite
kidney stone.

48
00:04:56,631 --> 00:04:58,549
Most kidney stones
are calcium and benign.

49
00:04:58,675 --> 00:05:00,593
Why would you
suspect a struvite stone?

50
00:05:00,718 --> 00:05:02,804
Because he said
kidney stones were boring.

51
00:05:02,929 --> 00:05:05,682
It's possible.
She's on birth control.

52
00:05:05,807 --> 00:05:07,850
Lots of sex could lead
to urinary tract infection,

53
00:05:07,976 --> 00:05:10,561
