struvite kidney stone.

54
00:05:10,687 --> 00:05:12,772
Excessive Antarctic drilling,

55
00:05:13,481 --> 00:05:15,358
bad for the environment
and the ladies.

56
00:05:15,483 --> 00:05:17,402
If it's a struvite stone, she
needs to break it up quickly

57
00:05:17,527 --> 00:05:19,112
