I like watching them blow stuff up.

67
00:05:47,974 --> 00:05:49,517
Who doesn't?

68
00:05:50,977 --> 00:05:52,145
That reminds me.

69
00:05:53,062 --> 00:05:54,814
Coma guy needs cable.

70
00:05:55,023 --> 00:05:57,423
Women's billiards is the only thing
that's keeping him alive.

71
00:05:57,525 --> 00:05:59,944
I'm sure Carlson will be moved
by his plight.

72
00:06:00,069 --> 00:06:02,321
