show that TV makes people happy.

81
00:06:21,924 --> 00:06:24,343
Premium channels
have a particularly striking effect.

82
00:06:24,469 --> 00:06:27,305
Charging patients for cable is bringing
in 13 grand a month.

83
00:06:27,430 --> 00:06:32,560
Until this injustice is righted,
I am going to waste 13 grand a day.

84
00:06:34,937 --> 00:06:37,356
That's $2.49 down.

85
00:06:38,274 --> 00:06:40,068
Get an EKG
and a cardiac enzyme.

86
00:06:40,193 --> 00:06:43,029
If those check out, discharge him,
and tell him to get a snow-blower.

87
00:06:44,781 --> 00:06:47,533
How much is 13 grand
divided by 4 cents?

88
00:06:48,451 --> 00:06:50,244
I am not giving you cable.

89
00:06:50,369 --> 00:06:53,169
You're gonna have to somehow survive
with the broadcast networks alone.

90
00:06:53,289 --> 00:06:55,374
I'll be fine on Tuesdays.

91
00:06:57,335 --> 00:06:59,695
If sound waves
from the flaw detector break the egg,

92
00:06:59,796 --> 00:07:02,006
it should safely dissolve
your kidney stone.

93
00:07:08,471 --> 00:07:09,806
<i>This isn't going to work.</i>

94
00:07:09,931 --> 00:07:10,973
Well,
there's no reason it shouldn't.

95
00:07:11,099 --> 00:07:13,392
Sound waves are sound waves.
Stones are stones.

96
00:07:13,518 --> 00:07:16,562
<i>Some are bigger than others.
Some are inside me.</i>

97
00:07:16,687 --> 00:07:18,773
How's it going, Team MacGyver?

98
00:07:18,898 --> 00:07:20,191
Oh, great.

99
00:07:20,316 --> 00:07:23,694
I can't get cable, but I can get
the South Pole on high-def.

100
00:07:23,820 --> 00:07:25,071
We're almost ready
to start the test.

101
00:07:25,196 --> 00:07:27,740
Test? Did Ford test the Edsel?

102
00:07:28,658 --> 00:07:33,287
Did Coke test New Coke? Did Shakespeare
test his final play, Snow <i>Dogs?</i>

103
00:07:33,412 --> 00:07:35,790
<i>I'm guessing you're Dr. House?</i>

104
00:07:36,833 --> 00:07:39,877
<i>I was wondering
when you might drop by.</i>

105
00:07:40,628 --> 00:07:41,629
Could she see me?

106
00:07:41,754 --> 00:07:42,839
<i>Oh, yeah.</i>

107
00:07:43,422 --> 00:07:45,633
You think Jagger shows up
for the sound check?

108
00:07:49,804 --> 00:07:51,848
Okay, roadies, off the stage.

109
00:07:53,015 --> 00:07:54,433
Go help Cameron in the ER.

110
00:07:54,559 --> 00:07:56,894
Why? No way you're just
doing her a favor.

111
00:07:57,019 --> 00:07:58,729
