to make a mistake.

113
00:08:00,565 --> 00:08:01,941
Find it so I can blackmail her.

114
00:08:03,276 --> 00:08:04,443
As far as you know,

115
00:08:04,569 --> 00:08:08,114
this is way more than just some silly
battle over cable.

116
00:08:14,078 --> 00:08:15,496
<i>Ready.</i>

117
00:08:40,813 --> 00:08:43,191
You might wanna
dial it down a smidge.

118
00:08:44,775 --> 00:08:47,403
<i>I am not doing this.</i>

119
00:08:47,862 --> 00:08:50,948
<i>Your kidney stone theory hinges on me
having sex, but I...</i>

120
00:08:51,073 --> 00:08:53,576
