143
00:10:05,940 --> 00:10:07,108
I don't see a problem so far.

144
00:10:07,233 --> 00:10:10,111
If our choice is between pissing
House off or pissing you off,

145
00:10:10,236 --> 00:10:11,696
that's not much of a choice.

146
00:10:11,821 --> 00:10:14,365
