147
00:10:14,490 --> 00:10:16,242
you're gonna make
my life miserable.

148
00:10:16,367 --> 00:10:17,785
Yes.

149
00:10:17,910 --> 00:10:20,871
And you're telling me this so you won't
feel as guilty when you do it.

150
00:10:22,999 --> 00:10:24,208
Yes.

151
00:10:24,500 --> 00:10:27,253
Accommodating House's
every whim is not my job anymore.

152
00:10:27,378 --> 00:10:29,088
But it is ours.

153
00:10:29,630 --> 00:10:32,049
