168
00:11:19,055 --> 00:11:21,807
Means she would put
the <i>N</i> in her left arm.

169
00:11:21,932 --> 00:11:23,601
Catheter in the arm
makes it hard to bend the elbow,

170
00:11:23,726 --> 00:11:25,269
the way people do
when they drink.

171
00:11:25,394 --> 00:11:28,731
We have a limited supply of medication,
and I am not about to waste it.

172
00:11:28,856 --> 00:11:30,900
Last I checked you had
a limited supply of doctors.

173
00:11:31,025 --> 00:11:35,613
<i>Right before I got sick, one of my crew
members severed his femoral artery.</i>

174
00:11:35,738 --> 00:11:37,114
<i>He needs the cefuroxime.</i>

175
00:11:37,239 --> 00:11:38,574
<i>Right. He called dibs.</i>

176
00:11:38,699 --> 00:11:42,745
His need is definitive.
Mine is speculative.

177
00:11:43,412 --> 00:11:44,622
You're breathing fast.

178
00:11:44,997 --> 00:11:46,415
<i>It's because I'm pissed off!</i>

179
00:11:46,540 --> 00:11:49,460
Lift up your chin.
Show me your windpipe.

180
00:11:52,129 --> 00:11:54,131
<i>My chest hurts.</i>

181
00:11:54,256 --> 00:11:55,341
It's deviating to the left.

182
00:11:55,466 --> 00:11:56,906
