is collapsing.

183
00:11:56,967 --> 00:11:58,636
Cate, is anyone there with you?

184
00:11:58,761 --> 00:12:00,346
- Sean went to the <i>mess.</i>
- You need to call someone.

185
00:12:00,471 --> 00:12:02,515
There's no time.
Get a syringe and a needle.

186
00:12:02,640 --> 00:12:04,280
- Why am I doing that?
- Shut <i>up</i> and <i>look.</i>

187
00:12:06,560 --> 00:12:07,728
She could pass out.
She needs to...

188
00:12:07,853 --> 00:12:09,188
She needs
to re-inflate that lung.

189
00:12:10,106 --> 00:12:11,857
Okay. Now, pull out
the plunger.

190
00:12:11,982 --> 00:12:13,783
I want you to stab yourself
in your right side

191
00:12:13,859 --> 00:12:16,695
between the second and third rib,
in the midclavicular line.

192
00:12:19,698 --> 00:12:22,138
By the time we get someone else there,
you'll have suffocated.

193
00:12:22,159 --> 00:12:23,369
<i>Just do it.</i>

194
00:12:35,714 --> 00:12:37,995
See all the good stuff that happens
when you listen to me?

195
00:12:40,678 --> 00:12:42,430
<i>Means it's not a kidney stone.</i>

196
00:12:53,232 --> 00:12:55,359
<i>Right side pain, vomiting,</i>

197
00:12:55,484 --> 00:12:58,612
<i>and now a lung that gets traumatized
without any trauma.</i>

198
00:12:58,863 --> 00:13:00,364
<i>Sounds odd. Probably is odd.</i>

199
00:13:00,489 --> 00:13:02,241
<i>We should discuss this,
then call her back.</i>

200
00:13:02,366 --> 00:13:06,245
No, it's fine. I made sure we got
the South Pole long distance plan.

201
00:13:06,662 --> 00:13:08,622
Her latest kidney
function test shows...

202
00:13:08,747 --> 00:13:10,249
<i>I know what it shows. I ran it.</i>

203
00:13:10,666 --> 00:13:13,252
The more you interrupt, the longer my
grandstanding is going to take.

204
00:13:13,377 --> 00:13:16,130
Since when do you let patients
participate in differentials?

205
00:13:16,380 --> 00:13:18,820
Since the patient and her doctor happen
to be the same person.

206
00:13:19,258 --> 00:13:21,010
<i>Your kidney function
is still declining.</i>

207
00:13:21,135 --> 00:13:22,052
<i>Means
you have a kidney problem.</i>

208
00:13:22,178 --> 00:13:25,639
But not one that needed antibiotics.
Makes us equally wrong.

209
00:13:25,764 --> 00:13:28,976
No.
Makes us both wrong. Not equally.

210
00:13:29,351 --> 00:13:30,895
You were at least six wronger.

211
00:13:31,812 --> 00:13:33,772
They run a PPD
before you shipped out?

212
00:13:33,898 --> 00:13:35,774
<i>On me and everybody else here.
It's not TB.</i>

213
00:13:35,900 --> 00:13:37,651
<i>Excuse us a second.</i>

214
00:13:39,069 --> 00:13:40,821
Cancer explains her symptoms.

215
00:13:40,946 --> 00:13:44,033
A tumor in her lung or kidney that threw
a clot to the other organ.

216
00:13:44,158 --> 00:13:47,578
And you're worried the tumor might
overhear, realize we're on to it.

217
00:13:47,703 --> 00:13:51,040
Cancer's a hard diagnosis for patients,
even when they're not in the South Pole.

218
00:13:51,165 --> 00:13:53,209
We should figure this out,
maybe bring Wilson in.

219
00:13:59,131 --> 00:14:01,258
<i>Obviously, you two think
I'm in bad shape.</i>

220
00:14:01,383 --> 00:14:03,594
- Only if you count the tumor.
- House.

221
00:14:03,719 --> 00:14:05,095
Probably in your abdomen.

222
00:14:05,763 --> 00:14:07,598
<i>But you don't have any advanced
imaging equipment.</i>

223
00:14:07,723 --> 00:14:09,403
<i>You also don't have
a surgeon to biopsy it,</i>

224
00:14:09,433 --> 00:14:11,227
<i>any stains to use on the slide,</i>

225
00:14:11,352 --> 00:14:13,229
<i>or an oncologist to analyze it.</i>

226
00:14:14,104 --> 00:14:15,856
<i>I'm too far away
to hold her hand.</i>

227
00:14:16,732 --> 00:14:17,900
<i>I have cancer?</i>

228
00:14:18,567 --> 00:14:19,610
Possibly.

229
00:14:19,735 --> 00:14:23,989
Since the only imaging equipment you
have is x-ray, let's start there.

230
00:14:24,114 --> 00:14:26,158
X-ray your entire body.

231
00:14:26,408 --> 00:14:28,327
<i>I'll upload the images
when I'm done.</i>

232
00:14:32,164 --> 00:14:33,916
Good for you.

233
00:15:01,151 --> 00:15:02,861
She's annoying.

234
00:15:03,153 --> 00:15:06,657
Refused to take the antibiotics because
other people might need them.

235
00:15:06,782 --> 00:15:09,451
She said she cares
about other people?

236
00:15:09,577 --> 00:15:10,786
