LE Prep. But she doesn't have any
controlled pore glass beads.

501
00:28:18,198 --> 00:28:20,075
You don't need them.

502
00:28:24,871 --> 00:28:26,271
<i>When you shake the test tube,</i>

503
00:28:26,331 --> 00:28:29,000
<i>the paperclip will damage
