results you'd never make a diagnosis.

514
00:28:56,152 --> 00:28:57,112
So, I'm wrong.

515
00:28:57,237 --> 00:29:00,448
You sleep like a baby.
Your life is unfolding as you dreamed.

516
00:29:00,573 --> 00:29:02,492
