517
00:29:02,617 --> 00:29:04,702
You don't change that
because people don't change.

518
00:29:04,828 --> 00:29:05,829
You want to believe that

519
00:29:05,954 --> 00:29:08,554
because then you're freed
from any responsibility for your misery.

520
00:29:08,623 --> 00:29:09,999
Oh, shut up.

521
00:29:10,917 --> 00:29:12,419
I get enough of this
from Wilson.

522
00:29:12,544 --> 00:29:14,064
