00:40:00,274 --> 00:40:02,985
<i>Bits of bone marrow have been
leaking into your bloodstream.</i>

725
00:40:03,110 --> 00:40:07,448
<i>Those fat emboli have caused blockages
in your kidney, lungs, and brain.</i>

726
00:40:08,407 --> 00:40:09,283
It doesn't even hurt.

727
00:40:09,408 --> 00:40:11,243
<i>Cold numbs everything.</i>

728
00:40:11,368 --> 00:40:13,954
Does a particularly great job
on the extremities.

729
00:40:14,080 --> 00:40:17,416
You'll need to close the break to stop
the marrow from leaking.

730
00:40:17,541 --> 00:40:18,959
This one you will feel.

731
00:40:20,002 --> 00:40:21,545
<i>Will you do it?</i>

732
00:40:22,379 --> 00:40:25,091
He drilled a hole in your
skull after drinking your pee.

733
00:40:25,216 --> 00:40:26,550
<i>I think he's up for this.</i>

734
00:40:26,675 --> 00:40:28,435
Grab the tip of her toe
with your right hand.

735
00:40:28,552 --> 00:40:30,346
Hold the break with the other.

736
00:40:30,471 --> 00:40:31,931
On the count of three,
pull hard.

737
00:40:33,557 --> 00:40:35,226
<i>One, two,</i>

738
00:40:35,601 --> 00:40:36,936
three.

739
00:40:46,195 --> 00:40:48,614
Splint your toe.
You'll be fine.

740
00:40:53,786 --> 00:40:55,496
Thank you, House.

741
00:40:56,831 --> 00:41:00,251
Don't thank me.
He's the one who saved your life.

742
00:41:27,820 --> 00:41:29,488
He likes her.

743
00:41:37,872 --> 00:41:41,500
A bottle of the Bordeaux
and some sparkling water.

744
00:41:46,964 --> 00:41:50,718
Well, you didn't pick her up,
which means she's coming from work, too,

745
00:41:50,843 --> 00:41:52,803
which means you're
comfortable enough to meet her.

746
00:41:52,887 --> 00:41:55,014
Damn. I thought I lost you
when I walked backwards

747
00:41:55,139 --> 00:41:56,473
through my own
footprints in the snow.

748
00:41:56,599 --> 00:41:59,643
I think I've got it narrowed down
to three possibilities.

749
00:41:59,768 --> 00:42:01,729
Better leave. If you see her,
it'll be cheating.

750
00:42:01,854 --> 00:42:03,147
It's not one of your ex-wives.

751
00:42:03,272 --> 00:42:04,398
Because they hate me.

752
00:42:04,523 --> 00:42:07,568
They don't. They should,
but they don't. I called them.

753
00:42:07,693 --> 00:42:10,237
It's someone new,
but someone I know.

754
00:42:10,362 --> 00:42:12,239
Did you ever consider
being happy for me?

755
00:42:12,364 --> 00:42:13,616
Briefly.

756
00:42:13,741 --> 00:42:16,118
You ordering the wine
before she got here...

757
00:42:17,369 --> 00:42:20,289
Girls are good, House,
and you know it.

758
00:42:20,414 --> 00:42:23,042
You solved your case
because you cared about that girl.

759
00:42:23,167 --> 00:42:26,337
You're demonstrating
the illusion of manly confidence,

760
00:42:26,462 --> 00:42:28,380
which means you haven't
closed the deal, yet.

761
00:42:28,505 --> 00:42:30,633
I closed the deal.
I just like her.

762
00:42:30,758 --> 00:42:31,884
Still?

763
00:42:32,009 --> 00:42:34,428
You knew your patient
hated having cold feet,

764
00:42:34,553 --> 00:42:38,098
because you did a physical exam,
because you liked her.

765
00:42:38,474 --> 00:42:42,519
Your theory is I cared,
therefore I let her keep her socks on.

766
00:42:42,645 --> 00:42:45,189
If that's what love is, then I don't
wanna have anything to do with it.

767
00:42:45,314 --> 00:42:48,067
It starts with warm feet,
but leads to other things.

768
00:42:48,192 --> 00:42:49,860
Your mom and I will explain
when you're older.

769
00:42:49,985 --> 00:42:53,113
If I'd made her take them off like I
should have, I'd have seen the toe

770
00:42:53,239 --> 00:42:54,399
and solved the case days ago.

771
00:42:54,490 --> 00:42:55,950
But you don't care about her.

772
00:42:56,075 --> 00:43:00,162
Of course not.
House doesn't care about anyone.

773
00:43:02,623 --> 00:43:04,250
Hi.

774
00:43:04,375 --> 00:43:05,584
Sorry I'm late.

775
00:43:07,503 --> 00:43:09,463
Cutthroat Bitch?

776
00:43:10,172 --> 00:43:14,260
I call her Amber.
Was she on your list?

